Contact Us
Thank you for considering Camelot Estates and Life Village, a Leased-Land 55+ manufactured home community in beautiful Ormond Beach, Florida. We are a Family-Owned business, and we take pride in what we do every day. Our Residents enjoy living in a well-cared-for and quiet community as we strive to live by our motto; "Happy Folks Live Here!" Take a moment to browse through our selection of our available
New Homes
,
Pre-Owned Homes
, and
Floor Plans
, or visit our
Gallery
to take a look around, or give us a call today to Schedule a Tour.
Our office is open weekdays from 8 AM-4 PM to answer any questions or concerns you may have. We Run both communities but solely operate from the Camelot Office. You can also email us after hours and we'll get in touch with you as soon as possible. We would love to hear from you!
